name: Kubu Carik - Karangasem Bali
address: HJP2+4M3, Banjar Kuhum, Ababi, Kec. Abang, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80852, Indonesia
review 1: Amazing place with a gorgeous view! The food is delicious and fairly priced. Everything is made fresh from local ingredients, that grow in the garden. Claudia and Kadek are very nice and make you feel at home. Loved all the pets they have there. Very quiet and relaxing!
review 2:
Great host, great room, great food, I love this place ! If I ever come back to Bali I'll definitely go there again. The view is just amazing.
If you're an animal lover you'll also love this place, there is about 4 dogs and plenty of cats and frog singing during the night.
review 3: Claudia and Kadek are beautiful people living in a beautiful part of the world! Spend 1 month with them and will never forget this time! Thank you for everything!
review 4: Everything was brilliant. You felt at home by the time you see the main gate. Everyone you meet there is awfully sweet. A hideout :)
